 Circuit Breaker 
 Acircuit breaker is a mechanical switching device capable 
of making, carrying and breaking the currents under normal 
condition   and   breaking   the   currents   under   abnormal 
conditions like a short circuit. 
Miniature circuit breaker (MCB) 
Aminiature circuit breakeris a compact mechanical device 
for making and breaking a circuit both in normal condition 
and in abnormal conditions such as those of over current 
and short circuit. 
Types of MCB’s 
MCBs are manufactured with three different principles of 
operation namely 
 a   Thermal Magnetic 
 b   Magnetic hydraulicand 
 c   Assisted bimetallic 
